In our initial implementation of keyboard events, we implemented these fields:

export interface INativeKeyboardEvent {
  altKey: boolean;
  ctrlKey: boolean;
  metaKey: boolean;
  shiftKey: boolean;
  key: string;
  eventPhase: EventPhase;
}

This isn't a complete list.  See:
https://www.w3.org/TR/uievents/#interface-keyboardevent

We need to go over this list and decide which of the remaining fields we should add support for.
